{"tid":1390183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民full gear 全民full gear 全民full gear 全民full gear 全民full gear","createTime":"2019-07-31T05:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T19:59:39.000Z","uid":116560,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"06ebf7794a5c3e02eb3abffa07bc0bf756b4de08","tid":1390183,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:42:29.000Z","msg":"全民full gear ！！！！<br />\n為左各位香港人安全，同為左所有因示威被捕既香港人，全民full gear出街！<br />\n而家個個示威完番屋企都要拋棄裝備，就係驚狗截查，而袋入面有裝備就係參與「衝擊」既證據。<br />\n但係，如果我地每個人，每日都帶裝備，捉到人有gear就唔係咩證據！<br />\n同black block 道理一樣，大家都有gear，就唔會累比人捉既手足因為有gear入罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ngear帶上身或者扣係袋，總之營造每人每日都拎裝備出街既氣氛！<br />\n<br />\n另外，為左隨時見到既癲狗，有裝備，隨時做好準備非常重要。葵涌警署現場大家不打算衝突，結果只有約10人有裝，係只有10人啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />結果狗都係亂吠亂咬人，保護自己，免受狗咬，出街帶裝備！！<br />\n<br />\n有人問你做咩出街都要帶齊裝，最簡單既理由，免受警察威脅人身安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n保護自己，保護手足，全民gear！"},{"pid":"42a39181d7af90edc0bc8146fed4b14d5d8f2152","tid":1390183,"uid":116560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:43:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc7c490fba9ed5623873a46791266c93697ca01","tid":1390183,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:44:44.000Z","msg":"全民full gear！"},{"pid":"ab34d84cc0852c9fe88655bc464e5cab53d64cd1","tid":1390183,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:45:36.000Z","msg":"全民上裝備！"},{"pid":"cde1960fca5ac634bca7dd79dd8c0dbfc91637e9","tid":1390183,"uid":59569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變做必需品"},{"pid":"d9beda232b2dab45d01100625073c8b7a9895e40","tid":1390183,"uid":116560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"頭盔眼罩豬嘴係基本配置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3e819f286603542ee4c7eab6e5c9560c05204a","tid":1390183,"uid":288351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:47:49.000Z","msg":"香港獨有fashion。<br />\n將佢油靚d先。"},{"pid":"6d033d24c9cdad123e86de34b36ed1a818ccd269","tid":1390183,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要威又要帶頭盔"},{"pid":"43b3f98af58310680052728c15286fcf5f9dbcde","tid":1390183,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af3e819f286603542ee4c7eab6e5c9560c05204a","tid":1390183,"uid":288351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:47:49.000Z","msg":"香港獨有fashion。<br />\n將佢油靚d先。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"太標奇立異小心比人認到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4476a0b8ce3ef4720974acc8fef21e1c68489c94","tid":1390183,"uid":706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:49:43.000Z","msg":"當黑社會著上制服<br />\n法律變左黑社會殺人放火既幫規<br />\n出黎遊行都被人告暴動<br />\n香港人，你仲等咩？<span style=\"color: red;\">係咪要被人綁實哂手腳被枝鎗指住個頭先開始考慮還拖？</span><br />\n<br />\n係無公義、政府無法無天既情況下，大王既說話絕對係真理<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xX22acO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxX22acO.png&h=81fead81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e09e195f1dabf3ab6a9230aabb40d6083142b55","tid":1390183,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re